quran[4{c,v,t}:
5,6,momino! jab tum namaz parhnay ka qasadkiya karo tum munh aur kohinyon taq haath dho liya karo aur sir ka maseh kar liya karo aur tikhno taq paon ( dho liya karo ) aur agar nahanay ki haajat ho to ( neha kar ) pak ho jaya karo aur agar bemaar ho ya safar mein ho ya koi tum mein se beeet al khala se ho kar aaya ho ya tum aurton se hum bistar hue ho aur tumhe pani nah mil sakay to pak matti lau aur is se munh aur hathon ka maseh ( yani tayamum ) kar lau. khuda tum par kisi terhan ki tangi nahi karna chahta balkay yeh chahta hai ke tumhe pak kere aur apni naematain tum par poori kere taakay tum shukar karo
5,7,aur khuda ne jo tum par ahsaan kiye hain un ko yaad karo aur is ehad ko bhi jis ka tum se qoul liya tha ( yani ) jab tum ne kaha tha ke hum ne ( khuda ka hukum ) sun liya aur quboolkiya. aur allah se daro. kuch shak nahi ke khuda dilon ki baton ( taq ) se waaqif hai
5,8,ae imaan walon! khuda ke liye insaaf ki gawahi dainay ke liye kharray ho jaya karo. aur logon ki dushmani tum ko is baat par amaada nah kere ke insaaf chore do. insaafkiya karo ke yahi parhaiz gari ki baat hai aur khuda se drtay raho. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
5,9,jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un se khuda ne wada farmaya hai ke un ke liye bakhshish aur ajar azeem hai
